2️⃣ Safeguard Sensitive Information
 Never share your passwords, private keys, or bank details with anyone. Always verify requests through official KuCoin channels.
3️⃣ Stay Alert for Scams
 Watch out for scammers who may send fake payment confirmations or impersonate KuCoin support. Be cautious and double-check all proofs.
4️⃣ Trust Your Instincts
If something doesn’t feel right, stop the trade immediately! Use the app to report any suspicious activity. Remember, it’s better to be safe than sorry.
